{
  "$comment": "Lab Map - Physical Topology Example. Fictional infrastructure for Meridian Systems — a small tech studio running self-hosted services in a colocation rack. Demonstrates physical cabling, switch port mapping, VLAN trunk assignments, and full hardware specifications across routers, switches, servers, NAS, and workstations.",
